T1  - The Long-Lasting Effects of Experiencing Communism on Attitudes toward Financial Markets
AU  - LAUDENBACH, CHRISTINE
AU  - MALMENDIER, ULRIKE
AU  - NIESSEN-RUENZI, ALEXANDRA
Y1  - 2026/04/01
PY  - 2026
